This is unacceptable and dangerous. I’m hearing reports that CDC and FDA workers are finding out if they still have a job only by if their badges let them into their buildings.

@RobertKennedyJr how do you plan to “make America healthy again” if you're firing the people who make sure our food and drugs are safe, who prevent infectious diseases, who try to prevent chronic disease, and who hold big tobacco companies accountable.

The question is not IF these cuts will harm people—it’s WHEN.

